  BeatId: tower_vista
  Text: "A tour on a toft, trieliche ymaked—narwe, lovelich and selcouth. Fro this elritch heght thou overlookest the fayr feeld ful of folke. Hier the drem is stille; no triaile stireth. The Tour of Trewthe and the world bynethe abyden."
